						               													<description>Lead your own game studio and create a cool game. Whether it is a masterpiece for a computer, console or mobile platform, the player decides.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the process, you will have to look for solutions for more than 60 cases based on real events, developed by professionals in the gaming industry, who have devoted themselves to developing games for many years and were able to recreate that indescribable atmosphere of chaos, fun, horror and extraordinary managerial decisions that are so inherent in game creators.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You need to create a game keeping the deadlines and meeting the expectations of investors. Only a well balanced team with a fighting spirit can succeed. &amp;#10;You need to keep track of the budget, maintain the team spirit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fixing bugs, closing gaps and so on - you need to overcome different difficulties to stay a successful game dev team and publish a new GAME.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;About authors of the game:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Golubkin Sergey - the owner of the board games publishing house GEMENOT, has released more than 30 desktops, an ex-producer of computer and mobile games in Ubisoft and Nival.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vyacheslav Utochkin is the director of educational programs for the gaming industry at the Higher School of Business Informatics of the Higher School of Economics, worked as a producer at the Mail.Ru Group on Armored Warfare, Perfect World and several other games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
